(24, 7, 'testinhggg', '<div class="head_box">Virtuos Corporation is headquartered in USA,&nbsp;with international presence/representation in Europe, Middle-East/Africa and APAC including Singapore, Australia and India, serving customers globally through a network of offices, Virtuos Consultants and partners present in major business destinations worldwide.</div>\n\n<div class="right_box_container"><img alt="History &amp; Background" src="http://www.virtuos.com/images/history_background.jpg" style="float:right" title="History &amp; Background" />\n<div class="q_box_container1" style="margin-top: 15px;">\n<div class="top">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div class="mid">\n<div class="bg">\n<div class="txt_container">Brief Background\n<ul>\n	<li>Founded in January 2008</li>\n	<li>Virtuos Global HQ: San Jose USA</li>\n	<li>Geo-Spread:US,EMEA,APAC,India</li>\n	<li>Co.Size: 50-200* staff</li>\n	<li><strong>Corporate website:</strong> <a href="http://www.virtuos.com" target="_blank">www.virtuos.com</a></li>\n	<li><strong>Blog:</strong> <a href="http://www.virtuosblog.com/in/" target="_blank">www.virtuosblog.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><em>*Including member companies</em></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class="footer">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>A top-notch team with nearly 15 years of leadership in the IT space, and over 100 man years of consulting experience assembled to form Virtuos. Armed with deep <a class="actor_link" href="../services/key_focus_areas.php" target="_blank">domain expertise</a> these innovators passionately built Virtuos around the new rules of the game &mdash; uncompromising, supremely self-confident, and great attitude. Talent, energy, ambition, intensity, ego, risk &mdash; these teams have it all in spades. And they play by a different set of rules. Thanks to the mantra given by <a href="http://www.bc.edu/schools/csom/faculty/bios/boynton.html" target="_blank">Andy Boynton</a> and <a href="http://www.imd.org/about/facultystaff/fischer.cfm" target="_blank">Bill Fischer</a> in building our teams truly as Virtuoso Teams.</p>', 'a:45:{i:0;s:1:"1";i:1;s:1:"2";i:2;s:1:"3";i:3;s:1:"4";i:4;s:1:"5";i:5;s:1:"6";i:6;s:1:"7";i:7;s:1:"9";i:8;s:2:"10";i:9;s:2:"11";i:10;s:2:"12";i:11;s:2:"13";i:12;s:2:"14";i:13;s:2:"15";i:14;s:2:"16";i:15;s:2:"17";i:16;s:2:"18";i:17;s:2:"19";i:18;s:2:"20";i:19;s:2:"21";i:20;s:2:"22";i:21;s:2:"23";i:22;s:2:"24";i:23;s:2:"25";i:24;s:2:"26";i:25;s:2:"27";i:26;s:2:"28";i:27;s:2:"29";i:28;s:2:"30";i:29;s:2:"31";i:30;s:2:"32";i:31;s:2:"33";i:32;s:2:"34";i:33;s:2:"35";i:34;s:2:"36";i:35;s:2:"37";i:36;s:2:"38";i:37;s:2:"39";i:38;s:2:"40";i:39;s:2:"41";i:40;s:2:"42";i:41;s:2:"43";i:42;s:2:"48";i:43;s:2:"57";i:44;s:2:"58";}', '2016-03-01 10:42:41');
